                                <td align="left" style="font-size:0px;padding:10px 25px;word-break:break-word;">
                                    <div style="font-family:Raleway;font-size:13px;line-height:1;text-align:left;color:#FFFFFF;">Attendees are not permitted to enter bunkrooms or lodges they are not assigned to without being accompanied by at least one resident. Day Pass attendees are not permitted in bunkrooms or lodge bedrooms.</div>
                                </td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <td align="left" style="font-size:0px;padding:10px 25px;word-break:break-word;">
                                    <div style="font-family:Raleway;font-size:13px;line-height:1;text-align:left;color:#FFFFFF;">All the residents in each bunkroom or lodge will be collectively responsible for the tidiness of their bunkroom or lodge, and they will be collectively responsible for any damage that occurs.</div>
                                </td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <td align="left" style="font-size:0px;padding:10px 25px;word-break:break-word;">
                                    <div style="font-family:Raleway;font-size:13px;line-height:1;text-align:left;color:#FFFFFF;">As bunkrooms and lodges are shared, residents of each bunkroom or lodge are expected to be mindful of their fellow residents. Behaviours that attract the objections of any other resident must cease immediately.</div>
                                </td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
